    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>In Hindu and Buddhist mythology, guardians. In Hinduism, guardians of the four cardinal directions. In Buddhism, the four heavenly kings and other protector spirits.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
